. ********************************
. 
. joinby one using `highered'

. assert _N==`k12n'*`hn'

. 
. 
. ********************************
. * Step 3: compute distance to colleges
. ********************************
. 
. geodist latitude longitude k12latitude k12longitude, gen(distance) miles

