. *********** clean qoi 35-40 as they have the same response options *************
. /* value labels for qoi 35-40
>  1 not at all true
>  2 a little true
>  3 pretty much true
>  4 very much true
> 
>  recode:
> -2 not at all true
> -1 a little true
> 1 pretty much true
